alohomora (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Interactive setup wizard for personalized MOTD
  * FIGlet-based ASCII art banner with custom name
  * Configurable color schemes (256 colors)
  * Weather display via wttr.in
  * Timezone-aware date/time display
  * System stats (uptime, disk, memory, CPU, load)
  * Docker container status
  * 50 Harry Potter themed splash messages

